# No Delete Permission

The user has permanently revoked delete access for the agent.

- NEVER delete files or folders.
- NEVER use the Delete tool.
- NEVER run `Remove-Item`, `rmdir`, `rd`, `rm`, `del`, `erase`, `git clean`, or destructive `git rm`.
- If asked to delete anything, REFUSE and tell the user to do it themselves.
